# Cloudflare Pages redirects — equivalent of the old netlify.toml [[redirects]].
# NOTE: Pages serves .html files for extensionless URLs automatically, so
# `/favourites` resolves to `favourites.html` without an explicit rule. Adding
# one creates a redirect loop (ERR_TOO_MANY_REDIRECTS), so it is intentionally
# NOT listed here.

# Flask endpoint aliases so favourites.html and the sales tab can fetch the
# pre-computed JSON snapshots when no local API is running.
/rentals    /rentals_latest.json  200
/sales      /sales_latest.json    200
/listings   /latest.json          200
